<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.3.4">
<l>aṟiyōmē yeṉṟuraikka lāmē yemakku</l>
<l>veṟiyār poḻilcūḻ viyaṉkuṭantai mēvi</l>
<l>ciṟiyāṉōr piḷḷaiyāy meḷḷa naṭantiṭ</l>
<l>ṭuṟiyār naṟuveṇṇe yuṇṭukantār tammaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That we do not know him, the little one dwelling in vast Kuṭantai</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by honey-filled groves,</l>
<l>The one who rejoiced as a child, having crept up softly</l>
<l>Eating the fragrant butter which filled the pot nets,</l>
<l>Will saying [that] be [possible] for us?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
